Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.23,0:02:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 凌·杰特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.66,0:03:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫·杜林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.17,0:03:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精神不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你來送我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.53,0:03:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來送行的就只有我一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.84,0:03:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人不來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.80,0:03:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要怪他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.19,0:03:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為太驚訝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.77,0:03:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然知道你上亞維的學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.01,0:03:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但沒想到你竟然是這種身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.36,0:03:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.46,0:03:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有告訴你們是我不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.17,0:03:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.37,0:03:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我說我是貴族的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.42,0:03:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們會讓我加入你們當中嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.54,0:03:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.81,0:03:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道你是那麼爛的選手的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.69,0:03:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不會讓你加入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.83,0:04:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.19,0:04:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是第一次啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.24,0:04:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道應該怎樣跟貴族交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.88,0:04:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.81,0:04:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.11,0:04:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這身裝扮很適合你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.08,0:04:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.08,0:04:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.77,0:04:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.03,0:04:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個阿姨好像看中你咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.62,0:04:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真另人羨慕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個中年婦女殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.65,0:04:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.72,0:04:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的臉給我多好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.08,0:04:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為帝國貴族打扮的地上人很稀罕而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像看見會用筷子的狗一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.54,0:04:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼狗嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.65,0:04:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的還是很帥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.82,0:04:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那是作為一個地上人來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.13,0:05:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.93,0:05:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.31,0:05:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在立體映像上看過亞維人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.41,0:05:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的全都是俊男美女嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.00,0:05:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.21,0:05:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有看過真人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.21,0:05:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想回來也肯定回不來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.21,0:05:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帝國會這麼輕易就封他為貴族嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.34,0:05:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也被騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.17,0:05:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是諷刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.73,0:05:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被關在動物園裡動物的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.57,0:05:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在能清楚地了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不明不白地來到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛有點習慣這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.46,0:05:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要到帝都留學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是要回故鄉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.78,0:05:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是要去軍隊事務官養成學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要成為軍人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.13,0:05:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是義務啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.49,0:05:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要繼承爵位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最少要在星界軍裡服役十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貴族看來也很辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.27,0:06:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身份越高被要求的義務也越大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.97,0:06:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起反過來還是比較合理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.48,0:06:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你也會登上軍艦之類的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.11,0:06:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.03,0:06:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,18點會來這裡接我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.90,0:06:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.82,0:06:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍艦會進入宇宙港嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.31,0:06:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿成這個樣子也是為了這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.14,0:06:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞維的軍人會來這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.68,0:06:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是亞維人就不清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是星界軍的軍士會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快到18點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.65,0:06:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.33,0:06:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是先離開的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.63,0:06:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不想看著我被帶走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.39,0:06:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.15,0:06:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會因為太過悲慘而流下憐憫的淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.22,0:06:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得可真好聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.56,0:06:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是戴爾庫圖上最沒良心的惡劣分子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.56,0:06:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要那樣誇獎我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.11,0:06:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很難為情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.78,0:07:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貴族的正式名字是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.87,0:07:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凌·蘇努＝洛克·海德伯爵公子·杰特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.66,0:07:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己的名字不是應該吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.22,0:07:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不習慣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.97,0:07:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得像是別人的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.26,0:07:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.03,0:07:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那……凌中略杰特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.73,0:07:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請記住我的名字庫·杜林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.73,0:07:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起凌什麼的杰特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總要好記得多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.13,0:07:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會忘記呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也把那個什麼的部分給忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好記住凌·杰特這個名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.04,0:07:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.10,0:07:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼凌·蘇努＝洛克·海德伯爵公子·杰特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.23,0:07:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是餞別禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…那個時候的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.35,0:07:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在行星戴爾庫圖的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.00,0:07:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要走了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.40,0:07:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.80,0:07:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.21,0:08:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.41,0:08:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你有個美妙的宇宙旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.58,0:08:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是是和美女服務員獨處就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.98,0:08:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.27,0:08:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起再美的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.64,0:08:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是喜歡跟你一起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.56,0:08:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得說出這衝擊性的表白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再繼續吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.73,0:08:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等下次回來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.10,0:08:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候我給你一個我公司的職位吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.70,0:08:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.85,0:08:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便能宣傳一下我們公司雇用了位帝國貴族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.78,0:08:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我還得謝謝你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.58,0:08:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杜林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.46,0:08:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.18,0:08:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後我一直目送他的背影消失在大門裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.38,0:08:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他到最後也沒有回頭看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰來抓住那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住那個強盜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.96,0:09:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的頭髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.06,0:09:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快抓住他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.54,0:09:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.35,0:09:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  為什麼會有亞維人追你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.73,0:09:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.06,0:10:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把皮箱扔掉  你會被亞維人殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.65,0:10:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會遇到這種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.98,0:10:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別殺我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我記住  亞維人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.57,0:10:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是凌·蘇努＝洛克·海德伯爵公子·杰特閣下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.60,0:10:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是……正是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 謝謝妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.27,0:10:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是從巡察艦哥斯羅斯號來接你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.32,0:10:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.41,0:10:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.86,0:11:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道我的名字吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.03,0:11:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是凌·蘇努＝洛克·海德伯爵公子·杰特閣下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.11,0:11:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.63,0:11:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是那個凌中略杰特沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我卻不知道妳的名字 這……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.11,0:11:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.55,0:11:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那感覺很奇怪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.28,0:11:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.23,0:11:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞維人該是怎麼樣的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我拉斐爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.75,0:11:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就像在做勝利宣言一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.45,0:12:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.62,0:12:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想稱呼你杰特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.17,0:12:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.24,0:12:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊……當然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.86,0:12:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這正是我求之不得的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.11,0:12:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是我的皮箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.95,0:12:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.48,0:12:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.73,0:12:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給 這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.27,0:12:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞維人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.68,0:12:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去 亞維人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.19,0:12:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.63,0:12:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.80,0:12:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帝國軍管理區域    嚴禁入內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.36,0:13:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.31,0:13:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.58,0:13:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛我敬禮的時候你向後退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.35,0:13:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.62,0:13:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊…那個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.65,0:13:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是故鄉的問候方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.47,0:13:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.57,0:13:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.21,0:13:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是害怕被打到而防禦一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.27,0:13:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.43,0:13:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是哪種文化看到不習慣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.24,0:13:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都會有奇怪的想法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 因為杰特也是亞維人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,習慣我們群星之眷屬的處事方式比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.56,0:13:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,群星之眷屬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為遺傳基因藝術產物的他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.05,0:13:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般都很漂亮且不會衰老
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有200年以上的壽命和藍色的頭髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.72,0:13:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更擁有能適應宇宙生活的體質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.74,0:13:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,群星的眷屬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.84,0:13:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與恒星共存的他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.92,0:13:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣稱呼自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.31,0:14:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我只是因為帝國的法規而被承認而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是哥斯羅斯號？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是開哪門子的玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.42,0:14:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是什麼都不知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.89,0:14:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是哥斯羅斯號搭載的短艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.79,0:14:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以坐下50人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.64,0:14:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天的乘客就只有你一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是我的榮幸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.14,0:14:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼由誰來操縱……算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.15,0:14:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…就這裡好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他的船嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副操舵席可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.82,0:14:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是 後面的客席呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會有美女服務員嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.14,0:14:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡雖沒有美麗的服務員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.33,0:14:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的操舵士倒是有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.68,0:14:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我坐副操舵席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.04,0:15:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣連上頭環
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.11,0:15:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能清楚宇宙船周圍的所有情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.26,0:15:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.31,0:15:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.08,0:15:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一就能感覺到船體感覺到的東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空識知覺真的那麼稀奇嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.12,0:15:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為在地上世界沒有能看見自己身後東西的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.25,0:15:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  這是我與生俱來的東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.26,0:15:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能看清嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.13,0:15:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快的速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.63,0:15:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.63,0:15:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這是為了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,思考結晶在檢測船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有奇怪的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.37,0:15:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會顯示為紅色並停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.96,0:16:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣操縱船  說實話讓人摸不著頭腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.75,0:16:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.27,0:16:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為  只有手指頭在動的操縱方式不覺得不合理嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.15,0:16:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你是說有更好的方式嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.63,0:16:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  比如那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不會突然想用左手去抓些什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.00,0:16:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.46,0:16:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是假設嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.88,0:16:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在操縱船的時候我會忘了左手的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.18,0:16:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘記……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.12,0:16:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看  這樣就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.80,0:16:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真簡單啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.43,0:16:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.39,0:16:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全靠思考結晶分擔了工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.84,0:16:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  機械也會有出錯的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.70,0:16:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人也會犯錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.66,0:16:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這句話真是讓人放心...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.65,0:16:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是太愛擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.99,0:16:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從剛剛開始就問這問那的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.25,0:16:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的機械怎麼可能這麼輕易就發生故障呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.09,0:17:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管制室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.56,0:17:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是行星戴爾庫圖第一宇宙港管制室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是巡察艦哥斯羅斯號艦載短艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.07,0:17:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艇指揮員的兵籍編號是01-00-0937684
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.62,0:17:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請求對第二軍用碼頭減壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.98,0:17:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.89,0:17:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥斯羅斯號艦載短艇  現在開始減壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.91,0:17:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個  看不到外面的樣子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.99,0:17:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想看嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.15,0:17:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.11,0:17:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒有空識知覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.93,0:17:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.47,0:17:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,減壓完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.00,0:17:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請求開放第二軍用碼頭閘門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.35,0:17:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白  哥斯羅斯號艦載短艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.77,0:17:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確認完全開放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.97,0:18:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請求出港許可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.75,0:18:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,允許出港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥斯羅斯號艦載短艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要使用電磁彈射嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.67,0:18:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要  使用低溫噴射推進出港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.11,0:18:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.95,0:18:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是電磁彈射的話你一定會眼花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.00,0:18:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥斯羅斯號艦載短艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.56,0:18:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿妳平安歸艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.22,0:18:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行星戴爾庫圖第一宇宙港管制室  完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.13,0:18:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.07,0:18:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥斯羅斯號艦載短艇  完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.06,0:18:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.21,0:19:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.84,0:19:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別把我當傻瓜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.99,0:19:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞維人的話  像這種飛船即使是小孩也能駕駛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看起來還很年輕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.56,0:19:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是說我看起來像小孩嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.84,0:19:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒有那個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 妳們的年齡很難分辨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.65,0:19:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且問女性年齡也很失禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.98,0:19:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.28,0:19:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的推理很正確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.62,0:19:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才剛剛滿16歲而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.70,0:19:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,16
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.91,0:19:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比我還小一歲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了可以加速的區域了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以加速嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.43,0:19:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.71,0:19:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要多久才到達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.47,0:19:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要看你能承受多大的加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是個地上人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.66,0:19:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳可以的話  我也應該可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.65,0:20:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  不用7分鐘就能到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.60,0:20:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.96,0:20:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…什麼 這是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.17,0:20:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加速啊  你不是說沒問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是像這樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.39,0:20:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.70,0:20:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要放慢一點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.74,0:20:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.19,0:20:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…為什麼會沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.63,0:20:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為祖先的船沒有重力控制系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.03,0:20:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是在高速下或是在無重力……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.98,0:20:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉斐爾～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.59,0:20:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 請快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.22,0:20:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.39,0:20:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 杰特
